name: Talk Nerdy with Cara Santa Maria

episodes.title: Corporate Sex Cult w/ Ellen Huet
episodes.description: In this episode of Talk Nerdy, Cara is joined by Bloomberg investigative journalist , and author, Ellen Huet. They discuss her 2025 book about OneTaste, Empire of Orgasm: Sex, Power, and the Downfall of a Wellness Cult . Follow Ellen: @ellenhuet
